Richard Charles Garnier1

M, #605014, b. 13 June 1950

Last Edited=3 Sep 2019

Consanguinity Index=0.49%

Richard Charles Garnier was born on 13 June 1950.1 He is the son of Colonel William d'Arcy Garnier and Hon. Lavender Hyacinth de Grey.2 He married Melissa Mary Denny, daughter of Anthony Meyrick Denny, in 1989.1

He was educated at Wellington College, Crowthorne, Berkshire, England.1 He was educated at University of Hull, Hull, Yorkshire, England .1 He lived in 2003 at Sarnden Farm House, Cold Harbour Road, Benenden, Cranbrook, Kent, England.1
